            "text": "<section class=\"trial-rules\" aria-labelledby=\"trial-rules-title\">\n  <style>\n    .trial-rules {\n      max-width: 720px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      font: 14px/1.6 system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n      color:#111;\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n    .trial-rules h2 {\n      font-size: 22px;\n      margin: 0 0 12px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n    }\n    .trial-rules h3 {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      margin: 20px 0 6px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .trial-rules p {\n      margin: 0 0 6px;\n      color:#555;\n    }\n    .trial-rules ul {\n      list-style: none;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n    .trial-rules ul li {\n      position: relative;\n      padding-left: 14px;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    .trial-rules ul li::before {\n      content: \"·\";\n      position: absolute;\n      left: 0;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <h2 id=\"trial-rules-title\">About The Program</h2>\n  <p>We want more people to experience Teslaunch products and services. By sharing your genuine experience, you help others better understand us. Please review the rules below before submitting your application.</p>\n\n  <h3>Product Scope</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>You may choose any product(s) from the T-Launch (formerly Teslaunch) store.</li>\n    <li>For YouTube reviews, the total product value must not exceed <strong>$200</strong>.</li>\n    <li>For reviews on other platforms, the total product value must not exceed <strong>$100</strong>.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Content Sharing</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Share an authentic product experience on your social media (text + video).</li>\n    <li>You agree that T-Launch (formerly Teslaunch) may repost your content on our official social media accounts.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Costs</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>No fees will be charged. T-Launch  covers both the product and shipping.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Authenticity Commitment</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>All information you submit must be true and valid.</li>\n    <li>Fraudulent submissions may result in legal action.</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
